Output docs/demo.gif
Set Shell "bash"
Set FontSize 14
Set Width 1100
Set Height 720
Set TypingSpeed 35ms

Type "pilot-agent version"
Enter
Sleep 1s
Type "pilot-agent setup --provider anthropic"
Enter
Sleep 1s
Type "pilot-agent init"
Enter
Sleep 1s
Type "pilot-agent run"
Enter
Sleep 2s
Type "/help"
Enter
